scenes.description: Nakiri Ayame and Sakura Miko performing 'Poppin' Candy ☆ Fever!'.
MC segment where Ayame and Miko discuss their performance and synergy.
Nakiri Ayame performing 'Watashi no Ichiban Kawaii Tokoro' with Usada Pekora, Houshou Marine, Shirogane Noel, and Shiranui Flare.

subtitles.original: あー！ありがとー！大好き！よかったー！ありがとうございます！
subtitles.english: Ah-! Thank you-! I love you! That was great! Thank you so much!

subtitles.original: ということで、今日みこちに一緒に歌って踊ってもらいました！
subtitles.english: And so, I had Miko-chi sing and dance with me today!

subtitles.original: ありがとうございます！
subtitles.english: Thank you so much!

subtitles.original: ありがとう呼んでくれて！嬉しいです本当に。
subtitles.english: Thank you for inviting me! I'm really happy.

subtitles.original: 嬉しいです本当に。可愛いなあ。
subtitles.english: I'm really happy too. You're so cute.

subtitles.original: 今日もかわよだなあ。
subtitles.english: You're cute today too.

subtitles.original: え、ありがとう。みこちも可愛いよ。
subtitles.english: Eh, thanks. Miko-chi is cute too.

subtitles.original: 可愛いよ。そんなことない！
subtitles.english: You're cute. That's not true!

subtitles.original: 可愛いね！
subtitles.english: You're cute!

subtitles.original: そんなことない！あやめちゃん可愛いね！
subtitles.english: That's not true! Ayame-chan is cute!

subtitles.original: あ、本当？可愛いね！
subtitles.english: Ah, really? You're cute!

subtitles.original: てかあれだよね、みこちとは新衣装ぶり？こないだの。
subtitles.english: By the way, it's been since your new outfit reveal, right? Recently.

subtitles.original: あ、そうだね。みこの新衣装ライブに。
subtitles.english: Ah, that's right. For Miko's new outfit live.

subtitles.original: ねー、可愛かったよ。でも二人はちょっと初めてだよね。
subtitles.english: Yeah, you were cute. But it's our first time as a duo, right?

subtitles.original: そうなんだよ。二人はね、初めてなんですよ。意外とね。
subtitles.english: That's right. It's the first time for just the two of us. Surprisingly.

subtitles.original: え、なぜあやめちゃんはみこのこと呼んでくれたの？
subtitles.english: Eh, why did Ayame-chan invite Miko?

subtitles.original: え、実はね、あの...
subtitles.english: Eh, actually, well...

subtitles.original: ポッピンキャンディ☆フィーバーを聴いた時に、あ、絶対にみこちに合うって思ったんですよ。
subtitles.english: When I heard 'Poppin' Candy Fever', I thought, 'Ah, this definitely suits Miko-chi.'

subtitles.original: えー！だから一緒に歌いたいって思って誘っちゃった。
subtitles.english: Eh-! So I thought I wanted to sing it together and invited you.

subtitles.original: やったー！ありがとう！
subtitles.english: Yay! Thank you!

subtitles.original: じゃ、あやめちゃんはみこになつき始めてきたという...
subtitles.english: So, that means Ayame-chan has started to get attached to Miko...

subtitles.original: え、そういう目線なの？そういう目線なのよ。
subtitles.english: Eh, is that how you see it? That's how I see it.

subtitles.original: うん。お友達みたいな感じではなく。
subtitles.english: Yeah. Not like we're friends or anything.

subtitles.original: いやなんか愛玩動物みたいな。
subtitles.english: No, it's more like a pet.

subtitles.original: あ、そういう感じなのね。やったー。愛玩動物みたいな。
subtitles.english: Ah, I see. Yay. Like a pet.

subtitles.original: あの、みことあやめちゃんて意外とシナジーあるよね。
subtitles.english: Miko and Ayame-chan have a surprising amount of synergy, don't we?

subtitles.original: 意外とね。ちょっとカメラさんちょっと引きで見えますか？
subtitles.english: Surprisingly. Mr. Cameraman, can we get a wide shot?

subtitles.original: ピンクで意外と可愛いんですよ二人。
subtitles.english: The pink is surprisingly cute on us.

subtitles.original: ね、可愛い。色合いが良きです。
subtitles.english: Yeah, cute. The colors are good.

subtitles.original: あとはあれだよね、鬼とお巫女だからね。
subtitles.english: Also, it's because it's an Oni and a Miko.

subtitles.original: あ、もしかしてこれ退治される側ですか？
subtitles.english: Ah, is this the 'getting exorcised' side?

subtitles.original: 鬼は外！福は内！
subtitles.english: Out with the demons! In with good fortune!

subtitles.original: わー！ありがとう！ありがとうございます！このあとも見てね！
subtitles.english: Wow! Thank you! Thank you so much! Keep watching after this too!

subtitles.original: わたしの一番かわいいところ
subtitles.english: My Cutest Part

subtitles.original: あれ、気づいちゃいましたか？
subtitles.english: Oh, did you notice?

subtitles.original: 生まれて30秒で最初に聞いた言葉...
subtitles.english: The first words I heard thirty seconds after being born...
